eral Manager John W McLean Editor Joyce Rossignol womens Editor Published by the West Hartford Publishing Company Bice Clemow President Henry E Griffith Vice President Too Much Delay On School Budget The Board of Finance and Board of Education were sched uled to meet in joint session Wednesday night As this is written before the meeting one thing already can be said about it for certain It is being held too late The corresponding joint meet ing last year was held March 9 two and onehalf weeks earlier Final action on the 19571958 Board of Education budget was completed by the Council March"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-12-15T22:41:14.297Z", "group": ["ndnp/ct", "connecticut-state-library-hartford-ct-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn85009852/1958-03-27/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ct:batch_ct_carpsurprise_ver01:data:sn85009852:00517174907:1958032701:0138/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=280&w=208", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ct:batch_ct_carpsurprise_ver01:data:sn85009852:00517174907:1958032701:0138/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=560&w=417", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ct:batch_ct_carpsurprise_ver01:data:sn85009852:00517174907:1958032701:0138/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1120&w=834", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ct/batch_ct_carpsurprise_ver01/data/sn85009852/00517174907/1958032701/0138.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["east windsor", "connecticut", "hartford", "south windsor", "glastonbury", "new britain", "united states", "east hartford"], "location_city": ["new britain"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["hartford"], "location_state": ["connecticut"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "numbe